msgid "CSRF verification failed. Request aborted."
msgstr "CSRF potvrda nije uspjela. Zahtjev je prekinut."

#: app/src/weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:19
msgid ""
"This HTTPS site requires a 'Referer' header to be sent by your web browser, "
"but none was sent. This header is required for security reasons, ensuring "
"that your browser is not being hijacked by third parties."
msgstr ""
"Ova HTTPS-stranica zahtijeva da tvoj internetski preglednik pošalje "
"zaglavlje „Referer”, ali nijedno nije poslano. Zaglavlje je potrebna iz "
"sigurnosnih razloga, kako bi se osiguralo da netko drugi ne upravlja tvojim "
"preglednikom."

#: app/src/weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:22
msgid ""
"If you have set up your web browser to not send 'Referer' headers,  you need "
"to turn that on (at least for this site, HTTPS connections, or 'same-origin' "
"requests)."
msgstr ""
"Ako je internetski preglednik postavljen da ne šalje zaglavlja „Referer”, "
"moraš aktiviraj slanje (barem za ovu stranicu, HTTPS veze ili zahtjeve „same-"
"origin”)."

#: app/src/weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:26
msgid ""
"Our site requires a session cookie to make the forms work. This cookie is "
"required for security reasons, ensuring that your browser is not being "
"hijacked by third parties."
msgstr ""
"Naša web stranica zahtijeva kolačić sesije da bi obrasci radili. Kolačić je "
"obavezan iz sigurnosnih razloga, kako bi se osiguralo da netko drugi ne "
"upravlja tvojim internetskim preglednikom."

#: app/src/weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:29
msgid ""
"It might have happened that your session cookie expired due to inactivity. "
"This can easily happen for unauthenticated requests where session validity "
"is limited. You might want to try your intended action again in such a case."
msgstr ""
"Može se dogoditi da tvoj kolačić sesije istekne zbog neaktivnosti. To se "
"lako može dogoditi za neautentificirane zahtjeve kod kojih je valjanost "
"sesije ograničena. U tom slučaju ponovo pokušaj obaviti tvoju namjeravanu "
"radnju."

#: app/src/weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:32
msgid ""
"If you have set up your browser to not save cookies, you need to enable "
"saving them (at least for this site, or 'same-origin' requests)."
msgstr ""
"Ako je internetski preglednik postavljen da ne sprema kolačiće, moraš "
"uključiti njihovo spremanje (barem za ovu stranicu ili za „same-origin” "
"zahtjeve)."

#: app/src/weblate/templates/403_csrf.html:36
#, python-format
msgid "CSRF failure reason: %(reason)s"
msgstr "Razlog CSRF neuspjeha: %(reason)s"

