"Use this when repository files became out of sync with Weblate for some "
"reason."
msgstr ""
"Koristi ovo kada datoteke repozitorija iz nekog razloga nisu sinkronizirane "
"s Weblateom."

#: app/src/weblate/templates/js/git-status.html:209
msgid "Rescan"
msgstr "Snimi ponovo"

